  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Frame Breaker</i> is an independently developed top-down 2D precision platformer. With over 50 minutes of lofi music, you can enjoy it as a relaxing and casual experience or challenge yourself with its fast-paced, high-difficulty action. You'll face more than 60 carefully designed levels that test your skills and reflexes. Every successful completion brings immense satisfaction—if you get stuck, just keep trying!</p>",
